{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2480000/extras/title-gifs-steam_en_01.gif?t=1730390233\" /><br>When children enter this mysterious park at midnight, there\u2019s only one option: <strong>survive</strong>.<br><br>Nightshift Survival is a challenging rogue-lite game where you will face hordes of terrifying and relentless creatures in Millennium Park. What mysteries and dangers does this place hide?<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2480000/extras/umbrella.gif?t=1730390233\" /><br><br>Face enemies with various movement patterns, collect powerups to survive, and unlock achievements with new items and ways to play.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2480000/extras/title-gifs-steam_en_02.gif?t=1730390233\" /><br>Be a pacifist survivor or a hunter of the mysterious creatures with the 57 items, including weapons, trinkets, and collectibles available to build your best strategy to survive the insane nights.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2480000/extras/bubbles.gif?t=1730390233\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2480000/extras/title-gifs-steam_en_03.gif?t=1730390233\" /><br>There are 13 sinister enemies, ranging from harmless little toys to child-devouring mechatronic beasts, all eager to play with you. Face your fears through the nights to make it unscathed until 6AM and confront the bosses of each night.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2480000/extras/title-gifs-steam_en_04.gif?t=1730390233\" /><br>With 60 achievements, unlock new possibilities to make each playthrough unique and showcase your skills as a true collector.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2480000/extras/title-gifs-steam_en_05.gif?t=1730390233\" /><br>Play and replay with different combinations of items to take down enemies!<br><br>Besides everything already present in the game, get ready for planned new content. Many secrets will still be revealed in the upcoming chapters.<br><br><strong>Survive the night shift, if you can.</strong>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Survived the nightshift. Somehow.","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2480000/c953ae6141b4a5e648ad0550946dc468a7b7b48d.jpg"},{"name":"Not even close!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2480000/ff965bd7fb4a1f57224c2bad232a20c86faa732d.jpg"},{"name":"What happened??","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2480000/e1903f91d8efc83fdc17a3d778827ae64149d9e2.jpg"},{"name":"Bed time!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2480000/146e02a81b92ab09e34637a739a57812b0859009.jpg"},{"name":"Not again...","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2480000/261f30b75444ba1c87277a8d7eebc1df4aaa907a.jpg"},{"name":"A long night","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2480000/acc50da40e75cefa746eba0dbf388b477885dca7.jpg"},{"name":"Raining indoors","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2480000/adde91d2b442b8e5b8d02e3565b2f4bb634f1974.jpg"},{"name":"Juicy!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2480000/bc7d5bd481787cdecca4490a5ee5a499f1a786d8.jpg"},{"name":"Five stars","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2480000/7374d863339ef2139373d5b3e6be355698c07f81.jpg"},{"name":"Prestige","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2480000/f41bd2427565d0c446a6421eedc95